                            <span class="first-word">Hello</span>, and <span class="first-word">welcome</span> to my blog!
                        </p>
                        <p class="author-description-text">
                            My name is Ilona, and I am a consultant in alternative medicine. I have a medical education and a broad experience in the healthcare system. My passion for a holistic approach to health began as a result of my personal experience. I was diagnosed with cancer and went through a difficult three years journey and traditional medicine did not give me the answers I needed. It was a difficult and scary time, but I didn't give up. Instead, I turned to alternative medicine and began learning from Polina, a qualified naturopath with 40 years of experience in this field. Her deep knowledge of how the human body works and how to treat it with natural remedies gave me hope and inspired me. As a result, I am now in remission with a balanced immune system.
                        </p>
                        <p class="author-description-text">
                            As I continued to study holistic medicine, I realized that traditional medicine may not always provide answers to important questions related to health and well-being. A holistic approach to health involves looking at a person's organism as a whole, thus treating the root of a problem and not its symptoms. 
                        </p>
                        <p class="author-description-text">
                            I use various holistic approaches to help my clients achieve optimal health and well-being, including nutrition, immune system strengthening, and body detoxification, which is also an essential part of a holistic approach to health.
                        </p>
                        <p class="author-description-text">
                            My mission is to teach people how to achieve health and happiness through a holistic approach and give them the knowledge and tools to make smart decisions about their health and well-being. I am ready to help anyone who is seeking answers to questions related to health and well-being.
                        </p>
                        <div class="author-desctiption full-description">
                            <p class="author-description-text description-footer">
                                Thank you for joining me on this journey, and I look forward to sharing more with you soon.
                            </p>
